{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"542","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"《科技》跨產業結盟再升級，15T循環經濟聯盟成軍","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>16:48 2019/09/20<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>時報資訊 林資傑</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>台灣永續供應協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TASS</span>）及國際半導體產業協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>SEMI</span>）號召<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>15</span>個公協會，今（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>20</span>）日宣示組成「<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>15T</span>台灣永續供應循環經濟聯盟」，將以創新與踏實策略，攜手合作落實循環經濟、成就永續共榮平台，盼讓世界看到台灣產業團結，開創科技永續新格局。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>此次活動也邀請台灣循環經濟與創新轉型協會理事長樊國恕，進行「營造循環經濟的友善環境」專題分享，盼以不斷厚實的聯盟能量，成為跨產業的整合推手，持續以創新力建立產業標準機制，以形成持續創新發展的力量。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>2017</span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>年初成立的<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TASS</span>，以協助企業建立整合供應管理、運籌流程與資訊共享的永續供應發展標準為宗旨，同年邀請國際半導體產業協會、台灣電路板協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TPCA</span>）共組台灣<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>3T</span>大聯盟，見證半導體封測永續材料標準的推動及制定，攜手產業同仁深耕環境永續發展。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>台灣<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>3T</span>大聯盟去年號召台灣加工出口區電電公會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TEPZEEMA</span>）、台灣半導體產業協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TSIA</span>）共組<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>5T</span>聯盟夥伴，宣示跨產業循環經濟聯盟正式啟動。今年則持續壯大聯盟力量，攜手<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>15</span>家公協會共襄盛舉，讓聯盟穩步升級，盼促進產業加速轉型升級。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>新增盟友包括台灣永續能源研究基金會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TAISE</span>）、金融研訓院、中經院、金屬中心（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>MIRDC</span>）、產基會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>FTIS</span>）、台灣石化公會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>PIAT</span>）、永進會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>SCEDA</span>）、環發會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>EDF</span>）、台灣化學產業協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TCIA</span>）、台灣資源再生協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>FARR</span>）、台灣循環經濟與創新轉型協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>CEITA</span>）等。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>TASS</span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>理事長賴樹鑫表示，協會以創新、永續、共榮、踏實願景持續發展相關業務。明年<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>12</span>月<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2</span>～<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>4</span>日將於高雄舉辦「<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TASS 2020</span>亞洲永續供循環經濟會展」，為亞洲地區首次以優化供應鏈為主軸，並以產業成果及商業模式所展開的會展。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>賴樹鑫指出，希望藉此協助半導體、鋼鐵、石化、電路板、塑膠、機械設備、能<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>/</span>水資源及綠色環保等產業研發創新，並推動循環經濟模式暨產品高值化，結合科技發展及生態平衡，朝科技創新、環境永續、產業共榮、循環踏實的願景邁進。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>TASS</span><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>副理事長周光春表示，台灣需攜手更多夥伴打造共享平台，日月光文教基金會與<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TASS</span>共同合作，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2017</span>年下半年起每年舉辦<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>2</span>次「台灣永續供應循環經濟論壇」，邀請國內外專家學者發表專題及產業趨勢交流。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>周光春指出，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>TASS</span>結合中華採購與供應協會（<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>SMIT</span>）年會，<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>12</span>月<span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box;'>5</span>日將在高雄展覽館舉辦「採購供應與永續循環展覽暨國際論壇」，以協助政府推動政策與國內業者掌握市場契機為目標，持續升級產業永續發展。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;'><span lang='EN-US' style='box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微軟正黑體, sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微軟正黑體; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-varian